Find Your Packages Faster in the AppExchange Partner Console

Narrow your search results and find your connected packages faster on the Partner Consoleâ€™s Solutions page. Search for a package by name or ID, or by package version name, version ID, or version number.

Where: This change applies to the AppExchange Partner Console.

To access: Go to the Solutions page under Technologies in the Partner Console. All packages that are in orgs connected to the Console appear.

Search methods:

* Enter a partial or full package name or package version name.
* Enter a partial or full package ID or package version ID.
* Enter a partial or full package version number, such as 1.0.1.

You must have Manage Listings permission in the Salesforce Partner Community to access the AppExchange Partner Console.
title: Improve Package Search in AppExchange Partner Console
